A stylized gem icon featuring a gradient of colors representing the five gem tiers: a bright yellow center for the Legendary tier, surrounded by layers of gold, purple, pink, and light yellow to represent Epic, Rare, Uncommon, and Common tiers respectively. The gem should have a subtle 3D effect with light reflections, set against a clean white background. The overall design should convey a sense of value and excitement, suitable for a puzzle game logo.
